  "remarks": "Deputy Editor of the newspaper of the President's Administration and main propaganda newspaper «Sovietskaia Belarus». Responsible for relaying state propaganda in the printed press, which has supported and justified the repression of the democratic opposition and of civil society, systematically highlighted in a negative and derogatory way using falsified and untrue information, in particular after the Presidential elections in 2010.",
